
                              Dali Clock
                          by Jamie Zawinski

                    https://www.jwz.org/xdaliclock/

Written in 2022, this version uses GTK 3 and OpenGL.  Improvements over the
Xlib Classic version are:

  - Fonts are scaled to fill the window.
  - Animation is anti-aliased.
  - Has a GUI preferences panel.
  - Remembers last window size and position.
  - Countdown mode.

